Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.88,0:02:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:150884,150884}What?\NMaya's not back yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.45,0:02:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:152452,152452}No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.18,0:02:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:154187,154187}The audition is tomorrow,\Nbut I still haven't heard from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.25,0:02:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:159259,159259}Oh, can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.32,0:02:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:161327,161327}Tōtō University Medical Center
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.02,0:02:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:163029,163029}We haven't heard from her at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.43,0:02:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:165432,165432}Is that right?\NHaven't heard from her…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.20,0:02:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:172205,172205}Teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.44,0:02:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:174441,174441}Go pick her up immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.84,0:02:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:176843,176843}Otherwise, she might not return.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.66,0:03:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:199666,199666}Here she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.40,0:03:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:202402,202402}Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.14,0:03:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:216149,216149}Wh-What is she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.85,0:03:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:217851,217851}She's playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.35,0:03:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:220353,220353}Babies often play like that,\Nsmiling like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.86,0:03:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:233867,233867}She's totally become Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.20,0:03:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:236202,236202}She even forgot the day\Nof her important audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.07,0:04:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:243076,243076}Here, Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.52,0:04:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:255522,255522}Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.16,0:04:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:260160,260160}Rei, Sayaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.66,0:04:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:262662,262662}Maya, your audition is tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.13,0:04:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:265131,265131}Oh, it has been that long…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.77,0:04:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:271771,271771}Good bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.94,0:04:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:273940,273940}Good bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.90,0:04:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:275909,275909}Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.27,0:04:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:277277,277277}Mr., Mrs., I'll see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.94,0:04:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:279946,279946}She seems just like an ordinary girl like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.08,0:04:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:281081,281081}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.78,0:04:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:282782,282782}Good bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.19,0:04:50.19,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:290190,290190}Miracle Worker Audition
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.83,0:04:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:296830,296830}We will now start the audition\Nfor the role of Helen Keller.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.56,0:05:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:301568,301568}Here, we have the five candidates.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.83,0:05:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:304838,304838}What's wrong with that Kitajima Maya girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.80,0:05:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:308808,308808}She has scratches all over her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.07,0:05:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:311077,311077}Yeah, she looks like she just got out\Nof volleyball practice or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.51,0:05:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:314514,314514}The six judges are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.71,0:05:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:318718,318718}Mrs. Himekawa Utako, who has not arrived yet due to her delayed flight, will be joining us soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.99,0:05:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:329996,329996}Mrs. Himekawa is the mother of Ms. Himekawa Ayumi…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.80,0:05:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:333800,333800}…one of our candidates, but the selection process will be fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.63,0:05:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:337637,337637}It's easy to say "fair,"\Nbut, you know…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.14,0:05:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:340140,340140}Yeah, of course you'd have special feelings for your own daughter, wouldn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.04,0:05:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:344044,344044}Now, let's begin the first audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.84,0:05:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:346846,346846}Candidates, please change into your costume.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:349249,349249}This way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.22,0:05:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:355221,355221}Hey, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.99,0:06:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:360994,360994}It's been a month since they have parted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.73,0:06:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:364731,364731}An emotional moment for mother and daughter to rejoin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.91,0:06:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:379913,379913}Oh, they just passed each other by without even looking at one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.08,0:06:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:382082,382082}They'll remain as strangers as long as the audition continues.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.58,0:06:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:384584,384584}What a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.18,0:06:28.18,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:388188,388188}I know she has a strict eye for Ayumi's act, but I will do my best on my terms, on behalf of Mr. Purple Rose, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.96,0:06:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:398965,398965}The audition has started downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.51,0:06:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:410510,410510}Candidate number one,\NMs. Shiratori Reina, please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.04,0:06:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:413046,413046}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.04,0:06:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:415048,415048}Shiratori Reina.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.11,0:06:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:415115,415115}Please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.24,0:06:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:416249,416249}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.55,0:06:58.55,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:418551,418551}This is…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.82,0:07:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:421821,421821}The first audition is to play as Helen.\NPlease start.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.99,0:07:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:425992,425992}As Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.99,0:07:11.99,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:431998,431998}I know, she liked dolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.14,0:07:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:444144,444144}Candidate number two,\NMs. Hayakawa Akiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.61,0:07:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:445612,445612}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.51,0:07:32.51,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:452519,452519}Okay, I'll use the blocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.04,0:07:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:476042,476042}Kanaya Emi's play is\Ndifferent from the first two.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.27,0:07:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:479279,479279}She's about to use all the toys here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.18,0:08:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:481181,481181}It's rare to see an act like hers\Nthat doesn't bore the judges.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.08,0:08:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:486086,486086}Very dynamic, and it will be great on stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.25,0:08:13.25,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:493259,493259}Maya, I'm sure she feels insecure\Ngoing up against Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.26,0:08:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:501267,501267}Candidate number four,\NHimekawa Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.17,0:08:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:506172,506172}Play as Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.22,0:08:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:522222,522222}W-What is she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.55,0:08:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:524557,524557}She seems to be\Nplaying with her nails.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.16,0:08:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:534167,534167}I wonder how long\Nshe'll be like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.90,0:08:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:536903,536903}Hasegawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.17,0:08:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:537170,537170}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.57,0:08:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:539572,539572}That ball, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.30,0:09:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:540306,540306}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.24,0:09:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:543243,543243}It's okay.\NJust do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.72,0:09:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:561728,561728}Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.18,0:09:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:582182,582182}She had her eyes wide open without even moving her eyes off the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:585318,585318}I'm sure that's what Helen would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.33,0:10:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:600333,600333}I'm looking forward to seeing what kind of play the last candidate can show us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.37,0:10:03.37,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:603370,603370}Play as Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:612178,612178}Again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.18,0:10:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:614180,614180}What's going on with her\Nand Himekawa Ayumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.45,0:10:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:618451,618451}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.52,0:10:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:629529,629529}She's fell asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.79,0:10:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:631798,631798}That's unacceptable!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.39,0:10:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:632399,632399}What do you think this audition is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.50,0:10:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:635502,635502}Hey, you!\NHey—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.70,0:10:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:639706,639706}We told you to play as Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.57,0:10:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:643576,643576}Don't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.78,0:10:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:647781,647781}Hey, you!\NWhat…?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.32,0:10:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:657323,657323}Hey, just…!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.89,0:10:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:657891,657891}Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.16,0:11:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:660160,660160}Just look at her.\NHer hands, her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.63,0:11:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:664631,664631}She's playing, as Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.50,0:11:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:668501,668501}She's enjoying tearing the pages.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.20,0:11:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:671204,671204}An ordinary person would come\Nin here and play with the toys.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.57,0:11:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:676576,676576}That is common sense, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.74,0:11:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:678745,678745}But, if the real Helen were here,\Nwhat would she do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.54,0:11:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:680547,680547}Huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.24,0:11:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:683249,683249}She wouldn't notice that the toys were here at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.32,0:11:30.32,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:690323,690323}This girl and Himekawa Ayumi definitely possess extraordinary talent.
Comment: 0,0:11:45.70,0:11:45.70,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:705704,705704}Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:11:49.29,0:11:49.29,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:709291,709291}#Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:11:52.21,0:11:52.21,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:712212,712212}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.45,0:12:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:720453,720453}The meeting is about to start\Nin the third conference room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.86,0:12:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:728862,728862}They reported the results\Nfrom the second audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.66,0:12:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:731664,731664}It's the simulated acting\Non the actual stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.13,0:12:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:734134,734134}Shiratori Reina and Hayakawa Akiko have equal chances of passing or failing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.74,0:12:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:741741,741741}Kitajima Maya acted wildly, but the judges didn't like it much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.84,0:12:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:749849,749849}At this point, Kanaya Emi,\Nwith her dynamic acting…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.55,0:12:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:754554,754554}…and Himekawa Ayumi, who showed\Nimpressive emotion, are leading.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.99,0:12:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:758992,758992}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.30,0:12:48.30,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:768301,768301}The audition came to the last test.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.34,0:12:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:777344,777344}The judges will be here shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.44,0:13:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:780447,780447}Please wait here as Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.48,0:13:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:782482,782482}This is the last test.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.35,0:13:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:785352,785352}I wonder if anyone\Ncan pass this test.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.32,0:13:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:789322,789322}If anyone does,\Nthen she's the real Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.79,0:13:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:792792,792792}If not, let's vote for one of these two.\NHimekawa Ayumi or Kanaya Emi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.94,0:13:26.94,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:806940,806940}If I don't get this role,\Nthen Miss Tsukikage will expel me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.11,0:13:34.11,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:814114,814114}No, right now, let's focus only on being Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.45,0:13:38.45,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:818451,818451}It might be my last chance to be Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.95,0:13:42.95,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:822956,822956}I am Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.69,0:13:45.69,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:825692,825692}Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.86,0:13:47.86,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:827861,827861}I know she will meet\Nmy expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.19,0:13:52.19,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:832198,832198}Bidoro
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.30,0:13:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:836302,836302}Maya…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.07,0:14:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:843076,843076}Maya…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.21,0:14:10.21,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:850216,850216}Alarm
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.19,0:14:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:862195,862195}This can't be happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.69,0:14:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:864698,864698}Unbelievable.\NNo way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.55,0:14:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:888555,888555}It stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.32,0:14:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:889322,889322}I wonder what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.16,0:14:54.16,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:894160,894160}Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.52,0:14:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:896529,896529}The last test is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.83,0:14:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:897831,897831}What!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.99,0:14:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:898998,898998}Over?\NWhat do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.10,0:15:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:902102,902102}The alarm was the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.13,0:15:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:905138,905138}You were told at the beginning\Nto wait as Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.07,0:15:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:909075,909075}Given that, though, it is human nature to react to something like the loud alarm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.05,0:15:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:918051,918051}The ones who didn't react are either the real Helen, or the ones who can play the real Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.99,0:15:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:924991,924991}A long time ago, at the audition for "The Miracle Worker" in America, there was one girl who didn't react to a loud noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.69,0:15:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:932699,932699}The girl later became known as Patty Duke (Atson),\Nwho won an Academy Award at the age of 16.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.37,0:15:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:941374,941374}Now, we have two Pattys here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.14,0:15:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:945145,945145}I see. I didn't even notice\Nthat it was the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.11,0:15:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:949115,949115}Didn't notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.08,0:15:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:951084,951084}Yes. I was thinking this might be the last time I can play Helen, then I started to forget that I was Kitajima Maya, and then I knew the alarm was going off, but I didn't feel anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.42,0:16:02.42,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:962429,962429}This girl…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.89,0:16:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:964898,964898}What about you, Ayumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.20,0:16:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:967200,967200}I just played the role.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.93,0:16:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:969936,969936}You told me to wait as Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.27,0:16:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:972272,972272}Then what if it was a real emergency alarm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.17,0:16:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:975175,975175}I wouldn't have stopped until I was told to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.41,0:16:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:979412,979412}Great work, Ms. Himekawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.24,0:16:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:983249,983249}No wonder the critics call you a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.25,0:16:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:988254,988254}Judges, may I please be excused now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.09,0:16:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:993093,993093}Ms. Kanaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.12,0:16:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:995128,995128}There's no need for me\Nto be here anymore now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.16,0:16:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:998164,998164}Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.77,0:16:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1006773,1006773}Kanaya Emi, I would like to cast her someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.27,0:16:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1012278,1012278}No, I would like to lobby for\NHimekawa Ayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.88,0:16:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1015882,1015882}Just think about\Nthe acting audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.18,0:16:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1018184,1018184}Kitajima Maya's simple acting\Nis no comparison to hers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.08,0:17:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1021087,1021087}Yes, I would agree with him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.52,0:17:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1026526,1026526}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.76,0:17:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1028762,1028762}…Sullivan, it will bring merit to the theater just for these factors alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.86,0:17:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1029863,1029863}Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.99,0:17:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1030997,1030997}I don't mean to interrupt, but we shouldn't have had an audition if you use those criteria.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.63,0:17:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1036636,1036636}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.90,0:17:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1037904,1037904}The purpose of the audition is to judge solely by acting…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.04,0:17:21.04,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1041041,1041041}Argue all you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.94,0:17:22.94,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1042942,1042942}The executive director and the manager are on my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.67,0:17:25.67,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1045679,1045679}Besides, we have Himekawa Utako and myself; and we'll chose Himekawa Ayumi for Helen by 4 to 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.28,0:17:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1053286,1053286}I was very intrigued by Kitajima Maya's acting for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.45,0:17:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1057457,1057457}So was I.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.59,0:17:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1059592,1059592}I have high expectations that she will play Helen as she has never been played before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.49,0:17:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1063496,1063496}We can't run a business on just expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.26,0:17:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1066266,1066266}But…!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.80,0:17:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1066800,1066800}Enough said.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.73,0:17:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1068735,1068735}I say we put it to a vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.30,0:17:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1071304,1071304}Let's be democratic about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.84,0:17:57.84,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1077844,1077844}I'm scared. They haven't\Nmade up their minds yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.88,0:18:00.88,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1080880,1080880}Help me, Mother, Rei,\Neveryone… Sakurakōji…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.51,0:18:06.51,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1086519,1086519}Miss Tsukikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.72,0:18:09.72,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1089723,1089723}Why is it taking so long?\NWhat's going on inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.59,0:18:13.59,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1093593,1093593}I, Himekawa Ayumi, have so much insecurity and anxiety.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.73,0:18:20.73,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1100734,1100734}This girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.20,0:18:22.20,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1102202,1102202}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.16,0:18:23.16,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1103169,1103169}It's because Maya's my opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.40,0:18:26.40,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1106406,1106406}She's making me nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.37,0:18:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1112379,1112379}I see, they will vote to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.01,0:18:35.01,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1115015,1115015}Meeting in session
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.41,0:18:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1115415,1115415}It must be tough for Himekawa Utako.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.01,0:18:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1118018,1118018}She's torn between the love of a mother\Nand her pride as an actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.93,0:18:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1139939,1139939}I will read the votes now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.91,0:19:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1146913,1146913}Himekawa Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.34,0:19:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1149349,1149349}Himekawa Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.78,0:19:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1152786,1152786}Kitajima Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.02,0:19:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1156022,1156022}Kitajima Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.15,0:19:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1159159,1159159}Himekawa Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.46,0:19:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1162462,1162462}Kitajima Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.17,0:19:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1172172,1172172}Three to three.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.24,0:19:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1174240,1174240}The last vote will decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.81,0:19:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1177811,1177811}Them, I will read the last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.08,0:19:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1185085,1185085}Hmm…\NT-This is…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.98,0:19:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1187987,1187987}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.65,0:19:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1188655,1188655}Whose name is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.43,0:20:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1202435,1202435}Both names…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.40,0:20:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1205405,1205405}Who did this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.37,0:20:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1207374,1207374}It was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.14,0:20:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1209142,1209142}Utako.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.61,0:20:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1212612,1212612}I chose as the actress\Nwho will play Annie Sullivan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.94,0:20:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1215949,1215949}I'm sure Himekawa Ayumi will play the perfect the perfect Helen, but Kitajima Maya has an interesting possibility of playing Helen as she has never been portrayed before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.52,0:20:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1228528,1228528}I couldn't discard either from my choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.60,0:20:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1239606,1239606}I hereby announce the decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.77,0:20:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1243777,1243777}Helen Keller will be played by…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.94,0:20:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1246946,1246946}…Himekawa Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.18,0:20:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1255188,1255188}And, also, by Kitajima Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.76,0:21:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1265765,1265765}We decided to double cast them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.30,0:21:09.30,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1269302,1269302}Double cast?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.24,0:21:15.24,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1275241,1275241}With Ayumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.11,0:21:18.11,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1278111,1278111}With this girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.68,0:21:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1280680,1280680}They will take turns each day to play Helen Keller with Annie Sullivan, played by Himekawa Utako.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.98,0:21:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1287987,1287987}By the way, this play, "The Miracle Worker," might be nominated for acting awards by the Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.79,0:21:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1294794,1294794}Now, please greet each other in the spirit of cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.20,0:21:48.20,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1308208,1308208}Ayumi…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.67,0:21:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1312679,1312679}I won't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.48,0:22:02.48,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1322489,1322489}I will play Helen with Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.65,0:22:04.65,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1324657,1324657}Under Director Onodera…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.26,0:22:07.26,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1327260,1327260}…and with her mother as Annie Sullivan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.89,0:22:10.89,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1330897,1330897}I wonder if I can go on, as Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.50,0:22:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1339506,1339506}So, the decision has been made.
Comment: 0,0:22:50.36,0:22:50.36,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:1370369,1370369}Ending
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.54,0:23:03.67,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1377544,1383674}{\blur3}It is lonely by myself…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.67,0:23:09.76,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1383674,1389764}{\blur3}…and I almost stumble.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.76,0:23:21.77,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1389764,1401774}{\blur3}Somewhere calls me here,\Njust like a whisper in the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.77,0:23:33.91,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1401774,1413914}{\blur3}Purple light, shining down\Non the horizon…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.91,0:23:39.79,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1413914,1419794}{\blur3}…more surer than words…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.79,0:23:45.92,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1419794,1425924}{\blur3}…telling us gently…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.92,0:23:52.01,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1425924,1432014}{\blur3}…that we'll meet\Neach other someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.01,0:23:58.10,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1432014,1438104}{\blur3}Of course you can\Nfly from far away…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.10,0:24:04.11,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1438104,1444114}{\blur3}…for the dream\Non my cheek…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.11,0:24:10.07,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1444114,1450074}{\blur3\fad(0,500)}…belongs to you.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:57.54,0:23:03.67,Ending,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1377544,1383674}{\blur1}It is lonely by myself…
Dialogue: 1,0:23:03.67,0:23:09.76,Ending,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1383674,1389764}{\blur1}…and I almost stumble.
Dialogue: 1,0:23:09.76,0:23:21.77,Ending,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1389764,1401774}{\blur1}Somewhere calls me here,\Njust like a whisper in the wind.
Dialogue: 1,0:23:21.77,0:23:33.91,Ending,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1401774,1413914}{\blur1}Purple light, shining down\Non the horizon…
Dialogue: 1,0:23:33.91,0:23:39.79,Ending,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1413914,1419794}{\blur1}…more surer than words…
